title: This One’s Cursed • EP116
itunes:title: This One’s Cursed • EP116
description:
The ladies are sharing their true feelings about this episode. There’s bad. There’s ugly. Is there any good!? Yes. Sheryl Crow!


"Are you Strong Enough" to love Tree Hill despite this week’s flaws?


"All I Wanna Do" is find out what went on with Deb, because she "Can't Cry Anymore". We know Peyton and Lucas are end game but this week they have major “My Favorite Mistake" energy.

 

The Drama Queens won't hold back because they know "Everyday is a Winding Road" and sometimes you have to get lost to get found.
